snippet.title: Illusions (Colecovision) gameplay footage
snippet.description:
Well this is an interesting one. The levels are optical illusions, with the first being inspired by M.C. Escher. First your goal is to get several blobs to combine into one and enter a mirror. Then you want to split one up again.

Thanks to Justin for loaning me this one.
http://www.youtube.com/user/jmtatari19
